* †''[[Boreomerope]]'' Novokschonov, 1995 (Siberia; extinct)
* ''[[Merope (insect)|Merope]]'' Newman, 1838 (USA, Canada)
* ?†''[[Thaumatomerope]]'' [[Alexandr Pavlovich Rasnitsyn|Rasnitsyn]], 1974 (Kyrgyzstan; extinct)
* †''[[Burmomerope]]'' [[David Grimaldi (entomologist)|Grimaldi]] & [[Michael S. Engel|Engel]], 2013 (Myanmar; extinct)
